These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: cola, juice, lemonade, water
Job: teacher, pilot, firefighter, electrician
1. Beverage:cola is on the right of Job:firefighter##1
2. Job:electrician is on the far left##1
3. Job:firefighter is between Job:pilot and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:water is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:lemonade is between Beverage:juice and Beverage:cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Job      | electrician | teacher | firefighter   | pilot |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
Pet: horse, goldfish, rabbit, rat
1. Pet:rat is between Hobby:reading and Pet:goldfish##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the far right##1
3. Pet:rabbit is on the right of Pet:horse##1
4. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Pet:horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Pet   | goldfish    | rat   | horse | rabbit       |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Music-Genre: r&b, salsa, rock, gospel
Nationality: australian, british, colombian, french
1. Nationality:colombian is on the right of Music-Genre:gospel##1
2. Nationality:colombian is between Nationality:british and Music-Genre:salsa##2
3. Nationality:british is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:french is on the left of Music-Genre:rock##1
5. Music-Genre:salsa == Nationality:french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre          | gospel    | r&b | salsa   | rock  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

 #################################
 
